mail-wizard-step-domain-title = Mail Domain
mail-wizard-step-tls-title    = TLS Certificates
mail-wizard-step-oidc-title   = Identity Provider (OIDC)
mail-wizard-step-confirm-title = Review & Confirm
mail-wizard-step-done-title   = Setup Complete

# ── Step descriptions ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

mail-wizard-step-domain-desc = Enter the primary mail domain and postmaster address (e.g. mail.example.com / admin@example.com).
mail-wizard-step-tls-desc = Choose between automatic TLS via ACME (Let's Encrypt) or provide your own certificate and key files.
mail-wizard-step-oidc-desc = Connect Stalwart to Kanidm for user authentication via OIDC. Users log in with their FreeSynergy account. This step is optional.
mail-wizard-step-confirm-desc = Review your configuration before writing it to disk and starting the Stalwart container.
mail-wizard-step-done-desc = Stalwart Mail has been configured successfully. Set the required DNS records shown below before your domain can send and receive mail.

